<plot>This is the fascinating story of Polish citizens who learn, often after living a lifetime as Christians in a Communist nation, that they are indeed of Jewish origin. Trapped between the familiar Polish world and an alien Jewish world, these "new Jews" often find themselves adrift in a country where religion and nationhood are inextricably linked.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?589270</url></doc>
